"<emphasis>DNS:</emphasis> provides <application>BIND9</application> DNS "
"server configuration options."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>DNS</emphasis>: fornisce le opzioni di configurazione per un "
"server DNS <application>BIND9</application>."

#: ../generic/serverguide/C/remote-administration.xml:437(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Objects:</emphasis> allow configuration of eBox <emphasis>Network "
